px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;">编辑：Aeneas 好困</span></p><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;"><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;"><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;"><h5 style="margin: 10px 8px 0px;padding: 10px;outline: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-size: 14px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;border-radius: 3px;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);line-height: 1.75em;word-break: break-all !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;visibility: visible;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;">【新智元导读】</strong>刚刚，Sora第二波视频放出了！稳定的一致性和模拟现实的逼真度，简直让人惊掉下巴。在好莱坞，已经有导演撤掉自己的8亿美元工作室扩建计划了。<strong style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;"></strong></span></h5></p></div></div><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">就在昨天，Sora又有全新「神作」炸出了！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">两位Sora作者，Bill Peebles、Tim Brooks纷纷甩出全新图片。（顺便还秀了一把</span><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration: line-through;">基</span><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">友情？）</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">「一只小熊猫和一只巨嘴鸟是最好的朋友，在蓝色时刻漫步在圣托里尼岛」，Peebles称这个场景简直就和两人走到OpenAI办公室的画面一模一样。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="185" data-backw="578" data-height="372" data-imgfileid="504964189" data-ratio="0.32037037037037036" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1160" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9UNicJchrBOkGHvBibt2zsnf3CptGpJaqgLdIanv1DwVp6ktAWdGmh2icA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="270" data-backw="480" data-imgfileid="504964191" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9VpiaiabR5hlKTJTsqDuv15ZTV3OedrK56Oe6yc5pwH9f7dibolgicianz4g/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">a red panda and a toucan are best friends taking a stroll through santorini during the blue hour</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这个视频的连贯性简直令人惊呼：在每一帧中，小熊猫和巨嘴鸟的形象始终保持着一致性。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">当然仔细看还是有不少破绽。比如小熊猫的腿有时会交织在一起，画面看起来更像卡通图像，而不像逼真的现实世界。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">但总的来说，这种视频质量已经足以让我们对AI视频的未来放飞想象。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">有网友立刻做出了配音版，贴切的配音一出，视频更有那个味儿了！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3344040089362120706" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9NlmHuHNCTGKbsf6Z0jdAqPpiawSDkW7Hr2J4fKXHtxXQm0DP26eNbZQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1280" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3344040089362120706"></iframe></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">难怪好莱坞大导Tyler Perry直言，自己在看完Sora制作的视频后，直接搁置了自己影师工作室8亿美元的扩建计划！</span></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">更多「神作」来袭</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这次两位作者放出的第二批视频，效果更加逼真、更加炸裂。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="480" data-backw="270" data-imgfileid="504964192" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="270" style="width: 57%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9u5aD6ibzruOlWuDyWP3SIdFC20UacfxHclYVzRFWxWOeic1WAaUe3OlA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">网友们接连不断发出惊叹：Sora是怎么做到一次比一次迭代得更好的？</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这个视频是「一名潜水员发现了一艘隐藏的未来沉船，里面有控制论海洋生物和先进的外星技术」。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="270" data-backw="480" data-imgfileid="504964193" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9Opy5VvVzQljtdeYxpRTZnFx5VczajhUKckerFiceg0K7KkII6LURk2w/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">a scuba diver discovers a hidden futuristic shipwreck, with cybernetic marine life and advanced alien technology</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">潜水员、海底景观、沉船外壳、内部的外星技术都生成得十分逼真。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">当然，这个场景也不是100%完美。立刻有人发现破绽——</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">比如，潜水员没有摆动脚蹼就能游动起来，也没有吐出气泡。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="110" data-backw="578" data-height="195" data-imgfileid="504964207" data-ratio="0.18950437317784258" data-type="png" data-w="1029" data-width="1029" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9ddU5uoxxECN22P8bm6icsfcaTqBA0zkl4AIZzAX0DZvjJAoSia5gTIHg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一位好莱坞电影制片人吐槽说：人的动作看起来没有灵魂，有些像僵尸。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="250" data-backw="578" data-height="450" data-imgfileid="504964208" data-ratio="0.4326923076923077" data-type="png" data-w="1040" data-width="1040" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9YeVAqLI2YiatWZtSq4mzicVaOxLbYK4WFoZZEWzfx1XxDkHjTDYhW0icg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">但对于不那么挑剔的观众，这个20秒视频的质量已经够了。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="93" data-backw="578" data-height="167" data-imgfileid="504964209" data-ratio="0.16135265700483092" data-type="png" data-w="1035" data-width="1035" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9OxdNDV2qv9HiaIuYFOJWmDfkGL3MRvdTmlB0qDoQibSGrd4eKflPCBGw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;">有人满意地说：看起来像《深海迷航》的高分辨率版本</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在以往，这个场景无疑要耗费巨资。而现在，好莱坞大片中烧金的高难度场景，都可以用Sora视频替代了，AI淘汰影视行业真不是说说而已！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这条闪着珠光的银色鳞片、有着冰蓝的眼睛和象牙龙角、吐出白气的小白龙，也让网友们惊呼，太太太震撼了！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="270" data-backw="480" data-imgfileid="504964194" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9WmRZPnf1N5eOtlGNYgtliaFIZO40sedkgCicYMZEpia24nfWEZhjG9yiag/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Close-up of a majestic white dragon with pearlescent, silver-edged scales, icy blue eyes, elegant ivory horns, and misty breath. Focus on detailed facial features and textured scales, set against a softly blurred background</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">它的拟人化做得很好，眼睛水汪汪的，传达了非常动人的情感，仿佛能听懂人话一样。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">《权力的游戏》中的巨龙，是这样的。跟它比起来，小白龙的差距并不太大。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="224" data-backw="400" data-height="224" data-imgfileid="504963931" data-ratio="0.56" data-type="gif" data-w="400" data-width="400" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr93I2HMpyyh09jZA0hHwic3748ADibn34xvkoveLhXtVIoibIFwzqo7XFnQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">有的网友表示，自己对这条小白龙爱不释手，直接给它配了个音——</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3344086434961702914" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9OH7AMzZJmWWfQ9WIJbU8Mhgqxy8TQIKOu6LxkXwSia9O0dB9QLs5c4g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1920" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.