kKwe5BG2MIiab8w/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">A surreal scene unfolds as a giant, translucent jellyfish floats gracefully through a deserted cityscape at dusk. The scene is shot on 35mm film</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这是一个精心制作的立体模型：江户时代，木结构建筑前，一个孤独的武士慢慢穿过小镇。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="270" data-backw="480" data-imgfileid="504964199" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9jz4GI5cQV9KKcgGIZCr4rIXkf5Vne0PhZvfYlrD9wmnwHtAuO6HgqA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">A meticulously crafted diorama depicting a serene scene from Edo-period Japan. Traditional wooden architecture. A lone samurai, clad in intricate armor, walks slowly through the town</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一只戴着护目镜的小胖哈巴狗，坐在一辆旧摩托车旁边的凳子上。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">仔细看可以发现，狗肚子一呼一吸的样子，显得非常真实。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="480" data-backw="270" data-imgfileid="504964200" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="270" style="width: 57%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9bic6c9UT024oVMQh3EqaWpOLBGLTRXAEUzYzLnQSSZNibxU6odLDOrGg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">a small chubby Pug dog in goggles is sitting on a stool next to an old motorcycle</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一只棕色边牧戴着太阳镜，滑着滑板。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="270" data-backw="480" data-imgfileid="504964201" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9noEcSOLw7F48YVqbCyf8spWsHq3HaQDmZEVvWcJ8bp6RDwEChY73bA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">a brown and white border collie stands on a skateboard, wearing sunglasses</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">可怕的事来了，有人在底下留言称，棕色边牧是自己的狗，这个视频是自己拍的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而我们，竟有那么一刻恍惚了：他说的究竟是真是假？</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="109" data-backw="578" data-height="168" data-imgfileid="504964188" data-ratio="0.18876404494382024" data-type="png" data-w="890" data-width="890" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9jMZDd0VHAdYbRkosGG8EcmRlWyOLXiaRWicjWfk2PJ2XEA3UiarAPib1kg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">总之，网友们迫不及待等待公测了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">还有人给Sora出了神考题——「一部手机正在直播进入黑洞的过程」。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="110" data-backw="578" data-height="164" data-imgfileid="504964187" data-ratio="0.19114219114219114" data-type="png" data-w="858" data-width="858" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9PqFFyhb0S7ZiaL5V7RicIe1WlC5TiaqZY83PibXRHnyEzy06EhJY1P8Fvw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">网友猜测：虚幻引擎被用来生成部分数据集？</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">随着这些视频被放出，网友们心中的疑问也越来越强烈——</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Sora模型究竟是用什么数据训练的？</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="92" data-backw="578" data-height="165" data-imgfileid="504964186" data-ratio="0.1588065447545717" data-type="png" data-w="1039" data-width="1039" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9xia91lt5xu3aA2VMdHIcwhTEVBshEehicKtibiaTmaNBnHl1ZibeweVibW4w/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">不少网友也觉得，怎么Sora生成的画面，看起来有些似曾相识？仿佛就是直接用虚幻引擎（Unreal Engine）做出来的一样。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-height="165" data-imgfileid="504963951" data-ratio="0.1588065447545717" data-type="png" data-w="1039" data-width="1039" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr98AIIMOEkRWtFYnF0hIcWlah9dBsgHKwtAqQ39EqLDQ11qBdH6WOtKw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">随后，越来越多人公认：Sora训练的数据集，应该就是用UE产生的。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="93" data-backw="578" data-height="165" data-imgfileid="504964185" data-ratio="0.16019417475728157" data-type="png" data-w="1030" data-width="1030" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9q6FhgVuXJmbSw22rIwuwa3uA8sMEp4Z6WI2L7s2UnD6XvxliajAqIwA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">其实，在Sora刚诞生时大佬就纷纷预测——Sora是由游戏引擎提供支持的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Pytorch联合创始人Soumith Chintala就这样认为。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="135" data-backw="562" data-height="259" data-imgfileid="504963953" data-ratio="0.23981481481481481" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9RicrDCdVr7GDMBw4ZM84u73E42S4dhfM1bAzKibQHpUkr3CZjEtcN4gw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">数据科学家和机器学习工程师Ralph Brooks也给出了自己的分析：</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="185" data-backw="578" data-height="372" data-imgfileid="504963973" data-ratio="0.32037037037037036" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1160" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9VQyibsMDxvFuStBoIQc7YbLFSwwNibo1BzwnS4VhYt6AutQGUf1BdtZA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">如果要创建大量不同角度的高清视频，就需要进行模拟。其中，有很多线索让我相信，UE5在一定程度上就是用来创建训练数据的。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">比如这段广为人知的樱花漫步视频中，人物移动的方式跟UE5中非常相似。现实中的人走路是不会用恒定速度的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="270" data-backw="480" data-imgfileid="504964204" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9PK2cArnlJ2ibfDkpex2D9twnibZg3ZL1lyiblOtQH2VLcS4gxkS1hObSg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">英伟达高级科学家Jim Fan同样表示，「如果Sora接受过大量UE5合成数据的训练，我不会感到惊讶的！」</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="260" data-backw="578" data-height="522" data-imgfileid="504963972" data-ratio="0.45" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1160" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9C8b8E06B98GIMto0Lko9nUgUGKkDx2MNfvRdvyq5hKa3G3wLurfHCg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">当然，它可能没有明确调用UE5，但非常有可能将UE5生成的文本、视频对作为合成数据，添加到训练集中。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="280" data-backw="578" data-height="562" data-imgfileid="504963971" data-ratio="0.4842592592592593" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1160" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9pLb0mqRH89OF7veLhVE6NqRER2mIdtbSbibfjw9z02MHukQ7lJw3Cibw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">早有预言帝猜中，Sora的推理管道是用的CLIP底座、文本转3D对象，和游戏引擎模拟。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="195" data-backw="578" data-height="392" data-imgfileid="504963969" data-ratio="0.33796296296296297" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1160" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr951UckYZ4FicMO79ibHNjz2zX7vOFPiaCiassWGNDE1VmbxIbPA47YhEicqA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">果然，「人工训练数据耗尽」不会阻止LLM的发展，合成数据才是AI的未来！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="70" data-backw="562" data-height="134" data-imgfileid="504963959" data-ratio="0.12407407407407407" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9dCK09t56ooiaHqDIB6sgTBF94PJ7A212RP6eEgFMvVsdW8NcIgEBR5A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">「精简版」体验，就藏在技术报告里！</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">网友们看到这些一代比一代强的demo，已经心痒难耐了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">好消息是：虽然Sora还没有正式开放功能，但在技术报告里，已经可以小体验一把了！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="162" data-backw="562" data-height="642" data-imgfileid="504963960" data-ratio="0.287962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2230" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9EMNe6hZPdXXQYfibQOMCXM2DicsYToFT3oU559umUd3FwcTuDwX8zkBQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;">报告地址：https://openai.com/research/video-generation-models-as-world-simulators</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">通过选择不同的关键词，比如人物、衣着、天气环境、地理位置等选项，就可以体验Sora生成的不同视频。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这样我们就可以看到——a穿着b样子的衣服，在c地点的d天气下，惬意地散步。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="160" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504964202" data-ratio="0.284375" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="960" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9xwaGcmKXoXiczicG3LeicMtsf1iaEVMyFkzyS9ibAI6cuD0Safpc7Ul0aQQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="160" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504964203" data-ratio="0.284375" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="960" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9SmWdfY2eSWLCVliaPErI2PDgmkvQ8H2pkEOspgvzLN2pHZjV8VDUU2w/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="160" data-backw="562" data-height="273" data-imgfileid="504963962" data-ratio="0.284375" data-type="gif" data-w="960" data-width="960" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9KTSMIEeHHic4XwlYoRYvLkJCO7rhyiaicpnZptPjChjO1jZIvh6DUOvicQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="160" data-backw="562" data-height="273" data-imgfileid="504963964" data-ratio="0.284375" data-type="gif" data-w="960" data-width="960" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9BTBKa7xfoaRKq9RPtpjLvicicjQYWTLYia0qKZgmcytAq4nXhNkrZ4Nog/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">好莱坞大佬直言很害怕，影视行业真完蛋了？</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这也难怪，好莱坞知名导演、制片人、演员Tyler Perry因为Sora，决定搁置自己亚特兰大工作室耗资8亿美元的扩建计划。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="155" data-backw="578" data-height="612" data-imgfileid="504963967" data-ratio="0.26851851851851855" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2280" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9o7cZL7iaghUnRZ8T4skWc0BzkTLhcCiclqicNCoTzjEbB3B9AjTLKPG3g/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">本来，Perry导演在过去四年里，一直计划斥资8亿美元扩建自己的工作室，为占地330英亩的土地增加12个摄影棚。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">然而，在2月16日看过Sora做出的视频后，他决定撤销自己的8亿美元计划，因为他拍摄的大片中，可能并不需要找取景地，或者搭建实景了。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">「以前，我们只是被告知AI可以做这些事，但是真的看到它做出来的场景，还是太令人震惊了！」</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="326" data-backw="578" data-height="730" data-imgfileid="504963968" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1296" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9nCemuYSsCESvAG92icAxZYV4558SywzBMIZWy7K1tLXWZIBUzO6nBwQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Perry导演表示，因为Sora给自己带来的冲击太过强烈，8亿美元扩建计划已被无限期推迟。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">现在，拍电影时再也不需要亲自前往拍摄地点了。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">不论是想要科罗拉多的雪地场景、月球上的场景，还是山中客厅中拍摄两个人的场景，都再也不要搭建真实布景，只要在办公室的电脑上，就能完成一切！</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而这也就意味着，巨大的变化将波及行业的每一个角落，影响到演员、灯光、运输、音效和剪辑等所有从业者的饭碗。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">现在，Perry导演已经在两部电影中的现场拍摄和后期制作中使用了AI，避免了耗费数小时给演员画老年妆。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Sora的出现彻底改变了游戏规则。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在以往，HBO的试播可能需要耗资1500万、2000万乃至3500万美元，而现在，这个成本低到不可想象。公司显然会选择成本更低的方案。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在不远的将来，很多工作岗位都会消失。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">影视行业该建立怎样的安全防护措施，保住大家的饭碗？</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;">参考资料：</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 14px;colo