r-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">相比之下，Midjourney的图是这样的：</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="315" data-backw="562" data-height="816" data-imgfileid="504963385" data-ratio="0.5601851851851852" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1456" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbibDpekvjc2lZE0ByXEjFcAT9KxVp5xU5Wf6LEoicdV46ShrRDyYMibTcg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Gemini Advanced / Ultra的图是这样的：</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="504963387" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbe4p9iab3wJ12biaRHfvicdBkU0nI1Owl3KOyKVIicXuO9YTGNVsQXCgIfg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">DALL-E 3的图是这样的：</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-height="1024" data-imgfileid="504963388" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="1024" data-width="1024" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbSUcsVGkIQdYvLkx0Y1fFLicYiaE0eYTeoJyAEVO4yvdSpBvnxccGVbOQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">各种形式的文字渲染，SD3 都出色地完成了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="538" data-imgfileid="504963386" data-ratio="0.5711252653927813" data-type="png" data-w="942" data-width="942" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbYAtFbOj25Cwia9OAhiblnZH1QMQT07IVE3iaZKDhO3XtIOlS8EuKqd0LA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt：Resting on the kitchen table is an embroidered cloth with the text 'good night' and an embroidered baby tiger. Next to the cloth there is a lit candle. The lighting is dim and dramatic.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：厨房桌上铺着一块精美的绣布，上面绣着「good night」字样和一只可爱的小老虎。旁边，一支蜡烛静静燃烧，散发出柔和而略带戏剧性的光影。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="686" data-imgfileid="504963389" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbM1sfjJWRx5VpMPUrGpVxy8Ke8VXiaLpm9kLSaNe99MGvcgicfbIyNvcQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt：Photo of an 90's desktop computer on a work desk, on the computer screen it says "welcome". On the wall in the background we see beautiful graffiti with the text "SD3" very large on the wall.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：一台放在工作桌上的90年代的台式电脑，屏幕上写着「welcome」。在背后的墙面上，有一幅醒目的涂鸦艺术作品，写的是「SD3」。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="686" data-imgfileid="504963390" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbr2Ww16E3typUficIh2SQbL0NAtkQU4koHibiae7cUbHJJFbrVUMNTne7A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Anime style illustration of a newsstand on top of a small grassy hill, on top of the newsstand we see the text "it's here!". In the background we see a big rain approaching.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：这是一幅充满动漫特色的插画，一个报刊亭坐落在一片绿意盎然的小山丘上，亭顶醒目地展示着「it's here!」的字样。而在这个宁静的场景背后，一场壮观的暴雨即将来临。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504963392" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb6yh1PaJjriaXflZ15tGWUUbD6OzGtYMX79JWkVMKSGYDMaFordFVN5w/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Night photo of a sports car with the text "SD3" on the side, the car is on a race track at high speed, a huge road sign with the text "faster".</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：在这幅夜幕下的摄影作品中，一辆标有「SD3」字样的运动赛车正在赛道上疾驰。背景里，一块巨大的路牌显眼地展示着「faster」一词。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="686" data-imgfileid="504963391" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb6AQnXnibbvpUwu2S1vokojSMv5icyx4yQzst7fdic6UplPaMGERKEic0gw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Three transparent glass bottles on a wooden table. The one on the left has red liquid and the number 1. The one in the middle has blue liquid and the number 2. The one on the right has green liquid and the number 3.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：一张木桌上摆放着三个透明的玻璃瓶。从左至右，每个瓶子内分别充满了鲜艳的红、蓝、绿色液体。瓶子上，用数字1、2、3进行了标记。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="686" data-imgfileid="504963393" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbxXpmh5Ikgm5AgrYTcFqE5MCyVCI8GbbibdX6f43MJ4VkFOHPLTicov7A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Photo of a rectangular orange neon sign with the text "even more stable", the sign is on the wall in a metro station, subway speeding by in the background, perspective photo.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Stable Diffusion 3.0能在文字渲染能力上取得显著提升，是因为Stability AI在新模型中采用了全新技术——Transformer和新增的文本编码功能。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">CEO Emad Mostaque解释说，因为上述原因，现在SD 3不仅能生成完整句子，还能保持风格的一致性。</span></p><h3 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">宇航员骑着粉色芭蕾舞裙猪，除SD 3竟然全军覆没？</span></strong></span></h3><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">处理包含多个对象的Prompt的能力，也是考核AI生图模型的一大关键指标。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">下面这个prompt，着实难倒了一大片选手——</span></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">一幅宇航员撑着粉色雨伞、骑着一只穿着芭蕾舞短裙的猪的画，猪旁边的地上是一只戴着高顶帽子的知更鸟，画面的角落里写着「stable diffusion」。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这个prompt，要求模型正确理解对象的属性、位置，以及正确呈现字体很小的文本，着实是一道难题。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">如此要素拉满的细节要求，SD3.0全部理解，并且精确地完成了！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">宇航员，粉色雨伞、穿着粉芭蕾舞裙的猪、戴高帽的知更鸟、角落里的字，100%符合prompt的要求。这就表明：模型很好地理解了prompt。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="768" data-imgfileid="504963394" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1344" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbFibKpBts2edxFEzERoIj3nqlNKeyTa2LPkyOM40eibhibHibOianMR9xVvg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: a painting of an astronaut riding a pig wearing a tutu holding a pink umbrella, on the ground next to the pig is a robin bird wearing a top hat, in the corner are the words "stable diffusion"</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">对于同一prompt，其他模型的表现就落后了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">DALL-E 3画出的画倒是过关了，但它把「Diffusion」拼错了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-height="1024" data-imgfileid="504963395" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="1024" data-width="1024" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbNyuiap2vptd8dwZW4NN8fm2amROC58iaKYp6OJ1eTBdURTG9ZQic1el8Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Bing的表现就更是离谱了，有的图中芭蕾舞裙的颜色不对，有的知更鸟站在了猪脑袋上，有的更是画面中飞满了知更鸟。而「Stable Diffusion」更是错得离谱。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="569" data-backw="562" data-height="1108" data-imgfileid="504963397" data-ratio="1.012962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1094" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbxSU6YgNFsAzROqiaqRU3ol8JoibXbtOsC9Z3yfCU7ljhbKUj8QLWaiaQg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Gemini Advanced这个差生的答案就更惨不忍睹了，除了拼写问题，画也没画对。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="512" data-backw="512" data-height="512" data-imgfileid="504963396" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="512" data-width="512" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbx84x7SUkmGZUPPaVdFibtyxXCXlibulFMA9XZXOZTEG5ibbWT7Sic2sg6A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">下面出场的，就是以画面质量精美著称的优秀文生图选手Midjourney了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">从画面美感上说，MJ依然甩其他模型一条街，但是考试就是考试，「Stable Diffusion」，它也没拼对。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="315" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504963398" data-ratio="0.5601851851851852" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbh1nb8hicIMUALicpdVE7ShARVsZxb7qajNnfFNPDoPfy3WBwIUMbkKGg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="315" data-backw="562" data-height="816" data-imgfileid="504963400" data-ratio="0.5601851851851852" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1456" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbwNrt5urShzVW8ZqDKwYibDznjy2eiakaA0kCFjRpFWENqf3ug7kophwA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">总结下来，这一道考题唯一的满分选手，就是Stable Diffusion 3！</span></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">和Sora同样的Diffusion Transformer架构</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">所以，Stable Diffusion 3.0为何有如此突飞猛进的表现？</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">原因在于，它采用了全新的架构设计。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Stability AI的首席执行官Emad Mostaque表示——</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">「Stable Diffusion 3 采用了Diffusion Transformer架构，这是一种新型的架构设计，与OpenAI最近推出的Sora模型采用的架构相似。」</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在以前的Stable Diffusion版本中，并未采用Transformer技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而Stable Diffusion 3.0采用了一种全新的方法，引入了Diffusion Transformer 技术。如果你对最近的爆火的sora有所了解，肯定对这个技术已经耳熟能详了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="461" data-backw="562" data-height="856" data-imgfileid="504963399" data-ratio="0.8199233716475096" data-type="png" data-w="1044" data-width="1044" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbertGCOq0t8aKj2ztJDQgk7z2rLCWJBqVABQF3ziaysmjqIcBrsdIgfQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Transformer技术是，当前生成式AI革命的核心，广泛应用于文本生成模型中。而图像生成技术，则主要基于Diffusion模型。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Sora作者之一William和谢赛宁，在这篇论文中共同提出了Sora的基础架构。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="515" data-backw="562" data-height="990" data-imgfileid="504963403" data-ratio="0.9166666666666666" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb52tnOlcUzOeuJUcaO7htAW9hvzVZNOtBRhV1x70FYxwGtZyZA2pvag/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;">论文地址：https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.09748</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这篇详细介绍DiTs的论文指出，这种基于扩散模型的新架构，可以用在图像patch上运行的Transformer替代了传统的U-Net架构。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这样，DiTs方法就可以更高效地利用计算资源，并且在图像生成方面超越了其他扩散模型技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一篇因「缺乏创新性」被CVPR 2023拒收的论文，竟成了Sora和Stable Diffusion 3.0的奠基之作，学术创新和工程创新的区别，着实引人深究。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="210" data-backw="562" data-height="430" data-imgfileid="504963401" data-ratio="0.3731481481481482" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1152" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbIX9bicjQNCicAJYibwtlriagFt9ZKKQ9Hnm9aSwxkW87uDEZXMbiaOXvqTA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Stable Diffusion 3.0 的另一个创新亮点，就是流匹配技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一篇关于流匹配的研究论文介绍了这一新方法，它可以用于训练连续归一化流（Continuous Normalizing Flows, CNFs），以便更准确地模拟复杂的数据分布。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="98" data-backw="562" data-height="182" data-imgfileid="504963402" data-ratio="0.175" data-type="png" data-w="1040" data-width="1040" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbMiaichtI0JIOuyLWyue7nDJzI7MQ97CJv9wOA5EOiaSoN6q6caMUMtrEA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;">论文地址：https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.02747</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">研究表明，通过结合使用条件流匹配（Conditional Flow Matching, CFM）和最优传输路径，可以实现更快的训练速度、更高效的样本生成，并且在性能上超越传统的扩散路径方法。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="580" data-backw="578" data-imgfileid="504963430" data-ratio="1.003125" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="640" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbwia07rYh6rcjk94F9LCB4j0321kwwmDg2DVZFG0FQ4kE6oib9otvsLPA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">其实，Stability AI一直在探索多种新颖的图像生成技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">就在本月初，他们就推出了一项名为Stable Cascade的新技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">它基于一种名为Würstchen的先进架构，旨在提升生成图像的性能和精确度。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="305" data-backw="562" data-height="1355" data-imgfileid="504963405" data-ratio="0.5416666666666666" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="2500" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbwb1PkhaTffqEApwQ5ib9pn4xn2p1TW7DIQqOxQPKUMsL66hMibBSUFtw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">一大波整活来了</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在图像质量上，SD 3.0也取得了令人震惊的进步。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">「变色龙在黑色背景上的摄影棚照片特写」，它生成的图是这样的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="768" data-imgfileid="504963406" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1344" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbVdBtqhZdXRsR1cEC2XyhCx8zfBNgqwpDhkah28ibbB0jMB9KztjJL9Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt：studio photograph closeup of a chameleon over a black background.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Gemini Advanced/Ultra生图是这样的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-height="1536" data-imgfileid="504963410" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1536" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbAqPDtmBHHUQRoKRbw2BynKhaib4va9gmJbXprUtp6B4OEHRhvR45v5A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Midjourney是这样的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="315" data-backw="562" data-height="816" data-imgfileid="504963408" data-ratio="0.5601851851851852" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1456" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb1JKe4AHjphn51mIcOvhQogr26ZDIibJXiaUU1LlL2Mbz1cZ9xOye8vUw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-s